🆕 v0.3 Highlights:
🌍 Room-Focused Exploration

Rooms have unique types: Corridor, Storage, Armory, Boss Lair

You progress room-by-room instead of racking up kills

👹 Boss Battles

Bosses appear in Room 5 and 10

Boss enemies are larger, more deadly, and have ASCII representation

💾 Save/Load System

Your progress is saved to a file: fps_save.dat

Load on start or reset progress
